<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٦٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5983">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يَحْيَى </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3447">‌عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> أَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6279">‌مَعْمَرٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6882">‌يَحْيَى بْنِ أَبِي كَثِيرٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">‌عِكْرِمَةَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَهَى رَسُولُ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ عَنْ بَيْعِ الْحَيَوَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٢٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بِالْحَيَوَانِ نَسِيئَةً».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>